---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/footer.astro';
import '../assets/css/contact.css';

const title = "Contact - AGWS";
const description = "Contactez-nous pour vos projets web et digitaux";
---

<Layout title={title} description={description}>
  <Header />
  <main class="contact-page">
    <section class="contact-hero">
      <div class="container">
        <h1 class="contact-title"><span class="highlight-text">Prendre contact</span> avec l'agence</h1>
        <p class="contact-subtitle">Discutons de votre projet digital ensemble</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="contact-content">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="contact-grid">
          <!-- Formulaire de contact -->
          <div class="contact-form-container">
            <div class="contact-form-header">
              <h2 class="form-title">Envoyez-nous un message</h2>
              <p class="form-subtitle">Nous vous répondrons sous 24h ouvrées</p>
            </div>
            
            <form class="contact-form" action="https://formspree.io/f/mldjelab" method="POST">
              <div class="form-row">
                <div class="form-group">
                  <label for="name">Nom complet</label>
                  <div class="input-wrapper">
                    <svg class="input-icon" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                      <path d="M20 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H8a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"></path>
                      <circle cx="12" cy="7" r="4"></circle>
                    </svg>
                    <input type="text" id="name" name="name" required placeholder="Votre nom">
                  </div>
                </div>

                <div class="form-group">
                  <label for="email">Email</label>
                  <div class="input-wrapper">
                    <svg class="input-icon" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                      <path d="M4 4h16c1.1 0 2 .9 2 2v12c0 1.1-.9 2-2 2H4c-1.1 0-2-.9-2-2V6c0-1.1.9-2 2-2z"></path>
                      <polyline points="22,6 12,13 2,6"></polyline>
                    </svg>
                    <input type="email" id="email" name="email" required placeholder="votre@email.com">
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="form-row">
                <div class="form-group">
                  <label for="phone">Téléphone</label>
                  <div class="input-wrapper">
                    <svg class="input-icon" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                      <path d="M22 16.92v3a2 2 0 0 1-2.18 2 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-8.63-3.07 19.5 19.5 0 0 1-6-6 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-3.07-8.67A2 2 0 0 1 4.11 2h3a2 2 0 0 1 2 1.72 12.84 12.84 0 0 0 .7 2.81 2 2 0 0 1-.45 2.11L8.09 9.91a16 16 0 0 0 6 6l1.27-1.27a2 2 0 0 1 2.11-.45 12.84 12.84 0 0 0 2.81.7A2 2 0 0 1 22 16.92z"></path>
                    </svg>
                    <input type="tel" id="phone" name="phone" placeholder="06 XX XX XX XX" 
                      pattern="^(?:(?:\+|00)33|0)\s*[1-9](?:[\s.-]*\d{2}){4}$"
                      title="Entrez un numéro de téléphone français valide">
                  </div>
                </div>

                <div class="form-group">
                  <label for="subject">Sujet</label>
                  <div class="input-wrapper">
                    <svg class="input-icon" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                      <path d="M21 16V8a2 2 0 0 0-1-1.73l-7-4a2 2 0 0 0-2 0l-7 4A2 2 0 0 0 3 8v8a2 2 0 0 0 1 1.73l7 4a2 2 0 0 0 2 0l7-4A2 2 0 0 0 21 16z"></path>
                      <polyline points="3.27 6.96 12 12.01 20.73 6.96"></polyline>
                      <line x1="12" y1="22.08" x2="12" y2="12"></line>
                    </svg>
                    <select id="subject" name="subject" required>
                      <option value="">Sélectionnez un sujet</option>
                      <option value="developpement-web">Développement Web</option>
                      <option value="e-commerce">E-commerce</option>
                      <option value="seo">Référencement SEO</option>
                      <option value="design">Image numérique</option>
                      <option value="domaine">Gestion de nom de domaine</option>
                      <option value="email">Emails professionnels</option>
                      <option value="maintenance">Maintenance web</option>
                      <option value="autre">Autre</option>
                    </select>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="form-group">
                <label for="message">Message</label>
                <div class="input-wrapper textarea-wrapper">
                  <svg class="input-icon textarea-icon" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                    <line x1="17" y1="10" x2="3" y2="10"></line>
                    <line x1="21" y1="6" x2="3" y2="6"></line>
                    <line x1="21" y1="14" x2="3" y2="14"></line>
                    <line x1="17" y1="18" x2="3" y2="18"></line>
                  </svg>
                  <textarea id="message" name="message" required placeholder="Décrivez votre projet..."></textarea>
                </div>
              </div>

              <button type="submit" class="submit-button">
                <span>Envoyer le message</span>
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                  <line x1="22" y1="2" x2="11" y2="13"></line>
                  <polygon points="22 2 15 22 11 13 2 9 22 2"></polygon>
                </svg>
              </button>
            </form>
          </div>

          <!-- Informations de contact -->
          <div class="contact-info-container">
            <div class="contact-card">
              <div class="contact-card-header">
                <h2 class="contact-card-title">Votre interlocuteur</h2>
                <p class="contact-card-subtitle">Discutez de votre projet avec notre équipe</p>
              </div>
              
              <div class="contact-details">
                <div class="contact-detail-item">
                  <div class="contact-icon-wrapper">
                    <svg class="contact-icon" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                      <path d="M20 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H8a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"></path>
                      <circle cx="12" cy="7" r="4"></circle>
                    </svg>
                  </div>
                  <div class="contact-detail-content">
                    <h3 class="contact-detail-title">Alexandre Grosse</h3>
                    <p class="contact-detail-subtitle">Dirigeant & Développeur</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="contact-detail-item">
                  <div class="contact-icon-wrapper">
                    <svg class="contact-icon" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                      <path d="M22 16.92v3a2 2 0 0 1-2.18 2 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-8.63-3.07 19.5 19.5 0 0 1-6-6 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-3.07-8.67A2 2 0 0 1 4.11 2h3a2 2 0 0 1 2 1.72 12.84 12.84 0 0 0 .7 2.81 2 2 0 0 1-.45 2.11L8.09 9.91a16 16 0 0 0 6 6l1.27-1.27a2 2 0 0 1 2.11-.45 12.84 12.84 0 0 0 2.81.7A2 2 0 0 1 22 16.92z"></path>
                    </svg>
                  </div>
                  <div class="contact-detail-content">
                    <h3 class="contact-detail-title">Téléphone</h3>
                    <a href="tel:+33625023130" class="contact-detail-link">+33 6 25 02 31 30</a>
                  </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="contact-detail-item">
                  <div class="contact-icon-wrapper">
                    <svg class="contact-icon" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                      <path d="M4 4h16c1.1 0 2 .9 2 2v12c0 1.1-.9 2-2 2H4c-1.1 0-2-.9-2-2V6c0-1.1.9-2 2-2z"></path>
                      <polyline points="22,6 12,13 2,6"></polyline>
                    </svg>
                  </div>
                  <div class="contact-detail-content">
                    <h3 class="contact-detail-title">Email</h3>
                    <a href="mailto:contact@agws.fr" class="contact-detail-link">contact@agws.fr</a>
                  </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="contact-detail-item">
                  <div class="contact-icon-wrapper">
                    <svg class="contact-icon" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                      <path d="M21 10c0 7-9 13-9 13s-9-6-9-13a9 9 0 0 1 18 0z"></path>
                      <circle cx="12" cy="10" r="3"></circle>
                    </svg>
                  </div>
                  <div class="contact-detail-content">
                    <h3 class="contact-detail-title">Localisation</h3>
                    <p class="contact-detail-subtitle">Paris, France</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
              
              <div class="social-links-container">
                <h3 class="social-links-title">Suivez-nous</h3>
                <div class="social-links">
                  <a href="https://github.com/grssalex/agws" target="_blank" class="social-link" aria-label="GitHub">
                    <img src="/img/git_logo.png" alt="GitHub" class="social-icon" />
                  </a>
                  <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/grssalex/" target="_blank" class="social-link" aria-label="LinkedIn">
                    <img src="/img/link.png" alt="LinkedIn" class="social-icon" />
                  </a>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- FAQ Section -->
    <section class="faq-section">
      <div class="container">
        <h2 class="faq-title">Questions fréquentes</h2>
        <div class="faq-grid">
          <div class="faq-item">
            <button class="faq-question" aria-expanded="false">
              <span>Quel est le délai moyen de réponse ?</span>
              <svg class="faq-icon" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                <polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"></polyline>
              </svg>
            </button>
            <div class="faq-answer">
              <p>Nous nous engageons à répondre à toutes les demandes sous 24h ouvrées. Pour les projets urgents, nous privilégions un premier contact téléphonique.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="faq-item">
            <button class="faq-question" aria-expanded="false">
              <span>Comment se déroule un projet web ?</span>
              <svg class="faq-icon" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                <polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"></polyline>
              </svg>
            </button>
            <div class="faq-answer">
              <p>Notre processus se déroule en plusieurs étapes : analyse des besoins, proposition commerciale, conception, développement, tests et mise en ligne. Chaque étape est validée avec vous.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="faq-item">
            <button class="faq-question" aria-expanded="false">
              <span>Proposez-vous un accompagnement après la mise en ligne ?</span>
              <svg class="faq-icon" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                <polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"></polyline>
              </svg>
            </button>
            <div class="faq-answer">
              <p>Oui, nous proposons différentes formules de maintenance et d'accompagnement pour assurer le suivi et l'évolution de votre projet.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="faq-item">
            <button class="faq-question" aria-expanded="false">
              <span>Quels types de projets réalisez-vous ?</span>
              <svg class="faq-icon" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                <polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"></polyline>
              </svg>
            </button>
            <div class="faq-answer">
              <p>Nous développons des sites vitrines, e-commerce, applications web, et proposons des services de refonte, d'optimisation SEO et de création d'identité visuelle.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
  <Footer />
</Layout>

<script>
  import '../scripts/contact-form.js';
  import '../scripts/faq-accordion.js';
  import '../scripts/theme-toggle.js';
</script> 